column5: Got out with a buddy to a nice fall spot ... same bait, same result... only better.  Gotta love it when a pattern comes together.  Big    Bigger     Biggest     Buddy's PB Bass   No scale on board ..... so I have no idea what they weighed but overall I think we boated a decent 18lb bag for the day... didn't even bother takin shots of the little guys.
Ottawa area ... if anyone is interested.
nice catch, good sized bass there!
What a basstactic Day!!! Congrats and thanks for the report. Was there one special bait or different patterns for that great day?  Cheers, 1leg
Great report and pics Seaweed  That's a real hog your holding on your last pic     Looks like you guys had a blast!  Congrats to your buddy for his PB  Thanks for sharing Leechman
Thanks, gotta love the topwater bite!
Great Report! Looks like the bass are starting to put on the feedbag!
